### Process a payment
POST https://localhost:7003/api/payments/process
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookingId": "{{bookingId}}",
  "userId": "{{userId}}",
  "amount": 899.97,
  "paymentMethod": "CreditCard",
  "cardNumber": "4111111111111111",
  "cardholderName": "John Doe",
  "cardExpiryMonth": "12",
  "cardExpiryYear": "2025",
  "cvv": "123"
}

### Test payment failure (card ending with 0000)
POST https://localhost:7003/api/payments/process
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookingId": "{{bookingId}}",
  "userId": "{{userId}}",
  "amount": 899.97,
  "paymentMethod": "CreditCard",
  "cardNumber": "4111111111110000",
  "cardholderName": "John Doe",
  "cardExpiryMonth": "12",
  "cardExpiryYear": "2025",
  "cvv": "123"
}

### Get a specific payment
GET https://localhost:7003/api/payments/{{paymentId}}

